<br>
I just have to wonder what is the cause for all the nerfs that went into these two patchs....<br>
<br>
Nerf Cleric Hammer<br>
Nerf Druid Epic <br>
Nerf Solo Experience (this was fixed after much bitching)<br>
Nerf to resistance<br>
Nerf Crit spell damage<br>
Nerf to pets being immune to charm<br>
Nerf Frenzy Burnout's explosion<br>
<br>
Other then the removal of the haste cap I see few positive things that went into this patch. This new version of Verant seems to be willing to wield the nerf bat as unforgiving as the old Verant crew. These changes (many unannounced) are totally uncalled for. I just wonder why did they do it?<br>
<br>
